content: For the future yes you should tag wrong number and strong harris. And wrong number response should work. But you can add the NV volunteer link.

How do we join the Slack texting channel while waiting for campaigns to be ported over to Discord? I can’t even find where to sign up for training but I’m an experienced texter and texted for Biden in 2020.
Well our text trainings are at capacity and we're only using  discord now.
Why do I not see any other text channels then?
I’m only in the text welcome
Because they're private. And only people with the role can see them.
Ok, so where would I “check back” for trainings to be posted or otherwise get added to the role?
How can I be added to the texting channel? I've participated in two trainings and am finally on discord
We can't add you right at this second. Maybe in a few days.

I registered for tonight’s training but never got a link and now it says at capacity, with no other times available. This morning there were six or eight dates available, but most weren’t until mid-September!
Have I been added to the texting channel. ?
